    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Photographs that purport to show personal energy fields (auras), energy or personality extensions (astral projections), pre- or postcognitive mental images, or various other supranormal visual manifestations.</Note_Text>
